edu.northwestern.at.utils
Class ArgumentList

java.lang.Object
  edu.northwestern.at.utils.ArgumentList

public class ArgumentList
extends java.lang.Object

ArgumentList.

ArgumentList provides methods for building an argument list for use in a DynamicCall.
